   Compiling playground v0.0.1 (file:///playground)
error[E0609]: no field `x` on type `&Point`
  --> src/main.rs:25:11
   |
25 |         a.x == b.x && a.y == b.y
   |           ^

error[E0609]: no field `x` on type `&Point`
  --> src/main.rs:25:18
